item.description:
Wed evening makeup, since the normal Mon evening is cancelled due to Hurricane Sandy.

This also happens to fall on Halloween. I guess you can show up in a costume if that's how you roll. I'll be dressing up as a gym climber.

Any skill level welcome - lead climbers and top-ropers as long as you've passed Metro Rock's belay test.

**********

Let's meet by the picnic benches. We'll pair up and get started no later than 7:15p.

I'll be the 5'7" Asian guy in a blue baseball cap.
item.name: MetroRock WED 10/31 [Halloween?]
